- annotate/document: MegaHttpClient, MegaChunkedCbcMac, MegaAesCtrEncryptor,
  MegaHttpInputStream

- MegaApi
  - cancellable API calls

- megadf:
  - show account subscription info

- streaming download/upload using the new API
  - MegaFileUploader
  - MegaFileDownloader
  - progress reporting

- filesystem querying (parent, children, filtering, globbing, paths)
- filesystem manipulation (rename, re-parent, add nodes)
- access rights (read-only/special cases)
- node tree/sub-tree sync optimization idea
- port tools to a new high-level api

- megareg:
  - present: http://g.static.mega.co.nz/pages/terms.html
  - interactive prompt for confirmation link

- megafs:
  - file reading/download
  - check that threads are used correctly in megafs

